headline.print_headline: Vettel to Leave Red Bull at End of 2014 Season
headline.main: Vettel to Leave Red Bull at End of 2014 Season

lead_paragraph: Four-time defending Formula One champion Sebastian Vettel will leave Red Bull at the end of the season and is expected to soon announce a deal with Ferrari.
